featured_reviews.review_id:
Siddhpur me Total 2 Ahle Sunnat ki Masjid He.
1) Mugal Datar Masjid
2) Gulista Park Masjid
Agar Aap Siddhpur ke Andar Bazar Me Jana chahte ho to Aap Mugal Datar Masjid me Namaz Padiye

Agar aap Main Highway per he Tab ye Masjid Sahi he Ye Masjid Dethali X se bahut Paas he Aap Chal kar 2-3 min me Pahunch Sakte he.

Gulista Park Masjid Me Dawat e Islami hind Ki Taraf se Imam Sahab he Unki Taqrir or Namaz Padhane ka Tariqa Bahut Pyara he. Or Masjid Me Washroom/ Toilet Ki bhi Service he.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
There are total 2 Ahle Sunnat Masjids in Siddhpur.
1) Mughal Datar Masjid
2) Gulista Park Masjid
If you want to go to the market inside Siddhpur then you can offer Namaz in Mughal Datar Masjid.

If you drive on the main highway and reach this Masjid within 2-3 minutes.

Dawat e Islami in Gulista Park Masjid from the side of Imam Sahab, his Taqrir or the way of offering Namaz is very lovely. Or there is also service of washroom/toilet in the mosque.
